Use the standard library
This is how to check_if_last_char_is_a_letter of txt:
   Remember that n is txt's length
   When n is 0, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when
   Remember that last is item (diff of n and 1) in txt
   When last is 32, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when
   The answer is 1
